author_ssm: Rhyannon J. Rodriguez, Rachel Greer, and Cristina Vignone.
unittitle_ssm: NIGHTCLUBBING Archive by Pat Ivers and Emily Armstrong
abstract_ssm: NIGHTCLUBBING was a weekly cable television show produced by video artists Pat Ivers and Emily Armstrong. The NIGHTCLUBBING Archive is a collection of videorecordings featuring live footage filmed between 1975 and 1980 that captures the burgeoning punk scene in nightclubs around New York City.
